    info <pack>                Show pack details and a sample of verbs (-v lists all)
    search <text>              Search packs by name or verb content (-v shows matching verbs)
    doctor                     Check for configuration problems
    version                    Print version
    completions <shell>        Generate shell completions (bash, zsh, fish)
    help [command]             Show help [for COMMAND]

  Options:
    --scope SCOPE Target scope: user (default), project, local, system
    --overwrite   Replace existing verbs instead of appending
    --force       Skip safety guards (re-apply or remove untracked packs)
    --all         Operate on all tracked packs (remove/update) or all scopes (status)
    --applied     Filter list to only applied packs (--scope filters to one scope)
    --dry-run     Show what would change without writing anything
    -v, --verbose Show detailed output
    -q, --quiet   Suppress non-error output
    --json        Output as JSON
    --no-color    Disable color output
    -n COUNT      Number of verbs to preview
    -V, --version Print version
    -h, --help    Show this help message

  Environment:
    NO_COLOR          Disable color output when set (any value)
    CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR Override Claude Code's config directory (default: ~/.claude)
